---
title: Grilled Mango-Chipotle Ribs and Feta-Buttered Corn with Sweet Potatoes and Asparagus
description: Sticky, sweet and with a touch of heat, these ribs don't need all day to cook. All they need is a kiss on the grill! Grilled corn with crumbled feta, asparagus and charred flatbread make this the perfect meal.
